{"tid":403620,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"(好奇一問) 九巴apps點樣定位啲巴士/預測到站時間","createTime":"2017-09-17T10:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T10:41:58.000Z","uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e383079d6f45fa08127a9352f3234ffa404ed269","tid":403620,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲預測時不時都唔準 勁多幽靈巴士<br />\ne.g. 即將到達變14分鐘<br />\n究竟佢點定位巴士同預測到站時間<br />\n<br />\n定位方法:<br />\n1)GPS定位加google map嘅tools預測到站時間 upload上cloud 每次到站update一次/每分鐘update一次<br />\n<br />\n2)ibeacon或類似嘅野放喺站度/巴士度 埋站時update位置<br />\n<br />\n3)巴士內置一啲裝置可以upload佢位置 e.g. 架車離開時如果broadcast下一站 就會同時update位置<br />\n<br />\n預測地站時間:<br />\n1)Google map API<br />\n2)用database搜集嘅平均到站時間(分hours)推算<br />\n3)Distance/avg. velocity of bus<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5886bc5a8965147c84ca90d0446fcae8d7aa3999","tid":403620,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:41:58.000Z","msg":"好似開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}